## Project Outcome

This repository simulates the complete workflow of a clinical research study, including protocol development, participant documentation, clinical data management, safety monitoring, regulatory compliance review, and final study reporting.

The project demonstrates practical knowledge relevant to Clinical Research Associate (CRA), Clinical Research Coordinator (CRC), Clinical Trial Assistant (CTA), Clinical Data Management, and Healthcare Data Analyst roles.
